     <td align="center" width="120" bgcolor="#dddddd"><font class="GraphicCaption">"You guys always have to bring me up when you talk about dissappointing quests, don't you?"</font></td>
     <td bgcolor="#ffffff"><img src="images/spacer.gif"></td>
